data.description:
Beautiful house across from pond featuring a kitchen that opens up to living room with granite counters, island and breakfast nook along with all updated appliances in 2022.  Living has fireplace with lots of windows.  Large Master Bedroom has whirlpool tub and separate shower. Split floor plan with new paint throughout most of the house. 
Large back yard with covered patio, new privacy fence in 2022.  3 car garage with (2) 220 outlets.  
Agent is related to Seller
